name: Tours White Executive Cool Vent
description:
This Tours White Exective Cool Vent Chef Coat is made of Poly/cotton with Cool Vent back yoke. The drop- shoulder coat is designed to look sophisticated whilst handling the culinary environment daily. It is long-sleeved, double-breasted with French cuffs and a cross-over collar with white piping detail. This multi-purpose coat also includes underarm vents and a left chest inset  as well as thermometer pocket. With hidden snap buttons and a thermometor pocket, this coat keeps you looking professional at all times. Sizes from XS-4XL.

This Tours White Exective Cool Vent Chef Coat is made of Poly/cotton with Cool Vent back yoke. The drop- shoulder coat is designed to look sophisticated whilst handling the culinary environment daily. It is long-sleeved, double-breasted with French cuffs and a cross-over collar with white piping detail. This multi-purpose coat also includes underarm vents and a left chest inset  as well as thermometer pocket. With hidden snap buttons and a thermometor pocket, this coat keeps you looking professional at all times. Sizes from XS-4XL.
